<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" itunes:timing="Word"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Answer"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="アンサー"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="KAF"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="kaf"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="かふ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花譜"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="花谱"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Magic"/><amll:meta key="album" value="魔法"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPZ922004451"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1688520966"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="1501450519"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="5w3rC66HQ8fQWg2V3gepdS"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="000qqSEZ0OMxiS"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="335544248"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="3:44.580"><div begin="19.460" end="3:44.580"><p begin="19.460" end="24.900" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="19.460" end="20.080">諦</span><span begin="20.080" end="20.250">め</span><span begin="20.250" end="20.440">る</span><span begin="20.440" end="20.700">こ</span><span begin="20.810" end="20.930">と</span><span begin="21.060" end="21.860">も</span><span begin="22.470" end="22.860">悪</span><span begin="22.860" end="23.050">い</span><span begin="23.050" end="23.220">こ</span><span begin="23.220" end="23.370">と</span><span begin="23.370" end="23.440">じ</span><span begin="23.440" end="23.790">ゃ</span><span begin="23.790" end="24.160">な</span><span begin="24.160" end="24.330">い</span><span begin="24.330" end="24.560">っ</span><span begin="24.560" end="24.900">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">“放弃也不是什么坏事”</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">「放棄也不是什麼壞事」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Saying that giving up isn&apos;t a bad thing either</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">포기하는 것도 나쁜 건 아니라고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Qu&apos;abandonner n&apos;est pas une mauvaise chose</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Dices que rendirse tampoco es algo malo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass Aufgeben auch nichts Schlechtes ist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que desistir não é algo ruim de se fazer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сдаваться тоже не так уж плохо</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Akirameru koto mo warui koto janai tte</span></p><p begin="25.480" end="29.360" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.480" end="25.690">あ</span><span begin="25.690" end="25.920">な</span><span begin="26.040" end="26.240">た</span><span begin="26.240" end="26.550">は</span><span begin="26.820" end="26.960">い</span><span begin="26.960" end="27.170">つ</span><span begin="27.170" end="27.410">も</span><span begin="27.730" end="28.110">笑</span><span begin="28.110" end="28.300">っ</span><span begin="28.300" end="28.490">て</span><span begin="28.490" end="28.650">言</span><span begin="28.650" end="28.860">う</span><span begin="28.860" end="29.070">け</span><span begin="29.070" end="29.360">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">虽然你总是笑着这样说</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">雖然你總是笑著這樣說</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You always say it with a smile but</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">너는 언제나 웃으며 말하지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu me le dis toujours en souriant mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque siempre lo dices sonriendo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sagst du immer mit einem Lächeln aber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você sempre diz isso sorrindo mas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ты всегда говоришь это с улыбкой но</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata wa itsumo waratte iu kedo</span></p><p begin="31.460" end="34.060" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.460" end="31.660">手</span><span begin="31.660" end="31.880">を</span><span begin="31.880" end="32.050">伸</span><span begin="32.050" end="32.200">ば</span><span begin="32.200" end="32.420">せ</span><span begin="32.420" end="32.800">ば</span><span begin="32.800" end="33.470">届</span><span begin="33.470" end="33.600">く</span><span begin="33.600" end="33.780">な</span><span begin="33.780" end="34.060">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但若伸出双手便能触及</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但若伸出雙手便能觸及</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If it&apos;s within reach when I stretch out my hand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">손을 뻗으면 닿는다면</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Si je peux l&apos;atteindre en tendant la main</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si al estirar la mano puedo alcanzarlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn ich es erreichen kann indem ich die Hand ausstrecke</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se eu puder alcançar apenas estendendo a mão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Если я могу дотянуться протянув руку</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Te o nobaseba todoku nara</span></p><p begin="34.480" end="40.690" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="34.480" end="34.870">紡</span><span begin="34.870" end="35.070">い</span><span begin="35.070" end="35.260">だ</span><span begin="35.260" end="35.650">今</span><span begin="35.810" end="36.560">ま</span><span begin="36.560" end="36.950">で</span><span begin="36.950" end="37.570">を</span><span begin="38.220" end="38.420">無</span><span begin="38.420" end="38.620">駄</span><span begin="38.620" end="38.760">に</span><span begin="38.760" end="38.980">す</span><span begin="38.980" end="39.170">る</span><span begin="39.170" end="39.350">わ</span><span begin="39.350" end="39.540">け</span><span begin="39.540" end="39.690">に</span><span begin="39.690" end="39.910">は</span><span begin="39.910" end="40.080">い</span><span begin="40.080" end="40.310">か</span><span begin="40.310" end="40.590">な</span><span begin="40.590" end="40.690">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我就不能让编织至今的一切付诸东流</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我就不能讓編織至今的一切付諸東流</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I can&apos;t let everything woven together until now go to waste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">자아낸 지금까지를 헛되게 할 수는 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je ne peux pas gâcher tout ce qu&apos;on a tissé jusqu&apos;ici</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No puedo desperdiciar lo que he tejido hasta ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Darf das bisher Gewobene nicht umsonst gewesen sein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não posso desperdiçar tudo o que construí até agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я не могу позволить чтобы всё сплетённое до сих пор было напрасным</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tsumuida ima made o muda ni suru wake niwa ikanai</span></p><p begin="42.920" end="45.120" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="42.920" end="43.320">何</span><span begin="43.320" end="43.690">度</span><span begin="43.690" end="43.860">だ</span><span begin="43.860" end="44.070">っ</span><span begin="44.070" end="44.240">て</span><span begin="44.240" end="44.430">悔</span><span begin="44.430" end="44.590">や</span><span begin="44.590" end="44.830">ん</span><span begin="44.830" end="45.120">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论多少次懊悔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論多少次懊悔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Regretting it over and over again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몇 번이고 후회하고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je regretterai maintes et maintes fois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Arrepintiéndome una y otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich bereue es immer wieder</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me arrependendo várias vezes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сколько бы раз я ни сожалела</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nando datte kuyande</span></p><p begin="46.310" end="48.810" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="46.310" end="46.690">何</span><span begin="46.690" end="47.060">度</span><span begin="47.060" end="47.270">だ</span><span begin="47.270" end="47.420">っ</span><span begin="47.420" end="47.820">て</span><span begin="47.820" end="48.450">歩</span><span begin="48.450" end="48.810">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论多少次前行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論多少次前行</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Walking on over and over again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몇 번이고 걸어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je marcherai maintes et maintes fois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Caminando una y otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich gehe immer wieder weiter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">E caminhando várias vezes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сколько бы раз я ни шла вперёд</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nando datte aruku</span></p><p begin="49.290" end="55.420" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="49.290" end="49.490">そ</span><span begin="49.490" end="49.660">の</span><span begin="49.660" end="50.060">度</span><span begin="50.060" end="50.350">に</span><span begin="50.760" end="50.970">突</span><span begin="50.970" end="51.130">き</span><span begin="51.130" end="51.880">放</span><span begin="51.880" end="52.320">さ</span><span begin="52.320" end="52.680">れ</span><span begin="52.680" end="53.790">る</span><span begin="53.790" end="54.010">か</span><span begin="54.010" end="55.420">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">正因为每次都被现实狠狠推开</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">正因為每次都被現實狠狠推開</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because I get pushed away every time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그럴 때마다 내쳐지니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car à chaque fois je me fais repousser</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque cada vez soy apartado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil ich jedes Mal weggestoßen werde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque toda vez sou empurrada para trás</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь каждый раз меня отталкивают</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono tabi ni tsukihanasareru kara</span></p><p begin="57.130" end="1:02.220" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="57.130" end="57.910">正</span><span begin="57.910" end="58.660">解</span><span begin="58.660" end="59.420">の</span><span begin="59.420" end="1:00.050">な</span><span begin="1:00.050" end="1:00.180">い</span><span begin="1:00.180" end="1:00.940">旅</span><span begin="1:00.940" end="1:01.260">を</span><span begin="1:01.260" end="1:01.680">し</span><span begin="1:01.680" end="1:02.130">よ</span><span begin="1:02.130" end="1:02.220">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">踏上这没有标准答案的旅途吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">踏上這沒有標準答案的旅途吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let&apos;s go on a journey with no right answer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">정답 없는 여행을 하자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Faisons un voyage sans bonne réponse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hagamos un viaje sin respuestas correctas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass uns eine Reise ohne richtige Antwort machen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vamos fazer uma jornada sem respostas certas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Давай отправимся в путешествие где нет правильных ответов</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Seikai no nai tabi o shiyou</span></p><p begin="1:02.780" end="1:09.170" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:02.780" end="1:03.200">変</span><span begin="1:03.200" end="1:03.400">わ</span><span begin="1:03.400" end="1:03.550">っ</span><span begin="1:03.550" end="1:03.740">て</span><span begin="1:03.740" end="1:03.950">行</span><span begin="1:03.950" end="1:04.100">く</span><span begin="1:04.100" end="1:04.310">こ</span><span begin="1:04.310" end="1:04.700">と</span><span begin="1:04.700" end="1:05.180">に</span><span begin="1:05.770" end="1:06.180">怖</span><span begin="1:06.180" end="1:06.570">が</span><span begin="1:06.570" end="1:06.700">る</span><span begin="1:06.700" end="1:07.130">必</span><span begin="1:07.130" end="1:07.670">要</span><span begin="1:07.670" end="1:08.020">は</span><span begin="1:08.240" end="1:08.420">な</span><span begin="1:08.420" end="1:08.600">い</span><span begin="1:08.600" end="1:08.830">か</span><span begin="1:08.830" end="1:09.170">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">没必要对不断变化感到恐惧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">沒必要對不斷變化感到恐懼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because there is no need to be afraid of changing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">변해가는 것을 두려워할 필요는 없으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car il n&apos;y a pas lieu de craindre le changement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque no hay necesidad de temer a los cambios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil du keine Angst davor haben musst dich zu verändern</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque não há necessidade de ter medo de mudar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь нет нужды бояться перемен</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kawatte iku koto ni kowagaru hitsuyou wa nai kara</span></p><p begin="1:09.870" end="1:14.340" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.870" end="1:10.660">正</span><span begin="1:10.660" end="1:11.460">解</span><span begin="1:11.460" end="1:12.040">の</span><span begin="1:12.170" end="1:12.740">な</span><span begin="1:12.740" end="1:12.930">い</span><span begin="1:12.930" end="1:13.650">日</span><span begin="1:13.650" end="1:14.080">常</span><span begin="1:14.080" end="1:14.340">へ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">通往没有标准答案的日常</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">通往沒有標準答案的日常</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">To an everyday life with no right answer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">정답 없는 일상으로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Vers un quotidien sans bonne réponse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hacia una cotidianidad sin respuestas correctas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In einen Alltag ohne richtige Antwort</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Rumo a um cotidiano sem respostas certas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">К будням где нет правильных ответов</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Seikai no nai nichijou e</span></p><p begin="1:14.760" end="1:21.050" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:14.760" end="1:14.980">そ</span><span begin="1:14.980" end="1:15.200">こ</span><span begin="1:15.200" end="1:15.550">で</span><span begin="1:15.550" end="1:15.920">は</span><span begin="1:15.920" end="1:16.170">き</span><span begin="1:16.170" end="1:16.320">っ</span><span begin="1:16.320" end="1:16.450">と</span><span begin="1:16.450" end="1:16.960">一</span><span begin="1:17.430" end="1:17.760">人</span><span begin="1:17.760" end="1:17.850">じ</span><span begin="1:17.850" end="1:18.950">ゃ</span><span begin="1:18.950" end="1:19.330">な</span><span begin="1:19.330" end="1:21.050">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在那里 我们一定不再孤单</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在那裡 我們一定不再孤單</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I surely won&apos;t be alone there</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그곳에선 분명 혼자가 아니야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Là-bas on ne sera sûrement pas seul</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Allí seguramente no estaré solo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dort bist du sicher nicht allein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Lá com certeza não estarei sozinha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Там я точно буду не одна</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soko dewa kitto hitori janai</span></p><p begin="1:21.920" end="1:27.400" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:21.920" end="1:22.280">間</span><span begin="1:22.280" end="1:22.880">違</span><span begin="1:22.880" end="1:23.060">い</span><span begin="1:23.060" end="1:23.320">を</span><span begin="1:23.780" end="1:23.940">間</span><span begin="1:23.940" end="1:24.390">違</span><span begin="1:24.390" end="1:24.580">い</span><span begin="1:24.580" end="1:24.820">で</span><span begin="1:25.310" end="1:25.450">終</span><span begin="1:25.450" end="1:25.680">わ</span><span begin="1:25.680" end="1:25.900">ら</span><span begin="1:26.000" end="1:26.300">せ</span><span begin="1:26.430" end="1:26.970">な</span><span begin="1:26.970" end="1:27.180">い</span><span begin="1:27.180" end="1:27.400">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">别让错误仅仅终结于错误</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">別讓錯誤僅僅終結於錯誤</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Don&apos;t let mistakes end as just mistakes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">잘못을 잘못으로 끝내지 마</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne laisse pas une erreur rester une erreur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No dejes que un error termine como un error</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass einen Fehler nicht als Fehler enden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não deixe um erro terminar apenas como um erro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не позволяй ошибке остаться ошибкой</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Machigai o machigai de owarasenaide</span></p><p begin="1:27.910" end="1:33.470" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:27.910" end="1:29.060">涙</span><span begin="1:29.060" end="1:29.340">を</span><span begin="1:29.810" end="1:30.560">涙</span><span begin="1:30.560" end="1:30.840">で</span><span begin="1:31.310" end="1:32.050">拭</span><span begin="1:32.050" end="1:32.320">わ</span><span begin="1:32.430" end="1:33.010">な</span><span begin="1:33.010" end="1:33.180">い</span><span begin="1:33.180" end="1:33.470">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">别用泪水去擦拭泪水</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">別用淚水去擦拭淚水</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Don&apos;t wipe away tears with more tears</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">눈물을 눈물로 닦지 마</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">N&apos;essuie pas tes larmes avec des larmes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No limpies las lágrimas con lágrimas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wische Tränen nicht mit Tränen weg</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não enxugue as lágrimas com mais lágrimas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не вытирай слёзы слезами</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Namida o namida de nuguwanaide</span></p><p begin="1:33.900" end="1:39.760" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:33.900" end="1:34.630">確</span><span begin="1:34.630" end="1:35.030">信</span><span begin="1:35.030" end="1:35.240">が</span><span begin="1:35.240" end="1:35.450">あ</span><span begin="1:35.450" end="1:35.750">る</span><span begin="1:35.750" end="1:36.090">そ</span><span begin="1:36.200" end="1:36.570">の</span><span begin="1:36.910" end="1:37.990">心</span><span begin="1:38.250" end="1:38.400">が</span><span begin="1:38.400" end="1:39.200">叫</span><span begin="1:39.200" end="1:39.380">ん</span><span begin="1:39.380" end="1:39.570">で</span><span begin="1:39.570" end="1:39.760">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">怀抱确信的那颗心在呐喊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">懷抱確信的那顆心在吶喊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That heart with conviction is screaming</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">확신이 있는 그 마음이 외치고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce cœur rempli de conviction hurle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ese corazón con convicción está gritando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieses Herz das sich sicher ist schreit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esse coração que tem certeza está gritando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это уверенное сердце кричит</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kakushin ga aru sono kokoro ga sakenderu</span></p><p begin="1:41.210" end="1:44.190" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:41.210" end="1:41.390">こ</span><span begin="1:41.390" end="1:41.600">こ</span><span begin="1:41.600" end="1:41.840">な</span><span begin="1:41.840" end="1:42.030">ら</span><span begin="1:42.280" end="1:42.470">も</span><span begin="1:42.470" end="1:42.540">う</span><span begin="1:42.790" end="1:43.150">一</span><span begin="1:43.150" end="1:43.310">人</span><span begin="1:43.310" end="1:43.390">じ</span><span begin="1:43.390" end="1:43.580">ゃ</span><span begin="1:43.700" end="1:43.990">な</span><span begin="1:43.990" end="1:44.190">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在这里 就再也不是孤身一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在這裡 就再也不是孤身一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If it&apos;s here I am not alone anymore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">여기라면 더 이상 혼자가 아니야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ici on n&apos;est plus seul</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si es aquí ya no estoy solo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hier bist du nicht mehr allein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se for aqui não estarei mais sozinha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Здесь я уже не одна</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koko nara mou hitori janai</span></p><p begin="1:55.460" end="2:00.880" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:55.460" end="1:55.700">や</span><span begin="1:55.700" end="1:55.880">れ</span><span begin="1:55.880" end="1:56.060">ば</span><span begin="1:56.060" end="1:56.220">で</span><span begin="1:56.220" end="1:56.450">き</span><span begin="1:56.450" end="1:56.770">る</span><span begin="1:56.770" end="1:57.010">か</span><span begin="1:57.010" end="1:57.790">ら</span><span begin="1:58.480" end="1:59.080">諦</span><span begin="1:59.080" end="1:59.230">め</span><span begin="1:59.230" end="1:59.280">ち</span><span begin="1:59.280" end="1:59.450">ゃ</span><span begin="1:59.450" end="1:59.710">ダ</span><span begin="1:59.830" end="2:00.180">メ</span><span begin="2:00.180" end="2:00.360">だ</span><span begin="2:00.360" end="2:00.570">っ</span><span begin="2:00.570" end="2:00.880">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只要去做就能做到 所以不能放弃啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只要去做就能做到 所以不能放棄啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Telling myself I can do it if I try so I shouldn&apos;t give up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">하면 되니까 포기하면 안 된다고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Qu&apos;on peut le faire si on essaie alors n&apos;abandonne pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Que si lo intentas puedes hacerlo así que no te rindas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dass ich es schaffen kann und nicht aufgeben darf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Que se eu tentar eu consigo então não devo desistir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Говорят что ты сможешь если попытаешься так что не сдавайся</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yareba dekiru kara akiramecha dame datte</span></p><p begin="2:01.480" end="2:05.290" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:01.480" end="2:02.060">何</span><span begin="2:02.060" end="2:02.270">度</span><span begin="2:02.270" end="2:02.500">も</span><span begin="2:02.810" end="2:03.400">心</span><span begin="2:03.740" end="2:03.930">で</span><span begin="2:03.930" end="2:04.710">笑</span><span begin="2:04.710" end="2:04.890">う</span><span begin="2:04.890" end="2:05.070">け</span><span begin="2:05.070" end="2:05.290">ど</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">虽然心中无数次以此自嘲</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">雖然心中無數次以此自嘲</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I laugh in my heart countless times but</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몇 번이나 마음속으로 웃지만</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;en souris souvent dans mon cœur mais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque me ría en mi corazón muchas veces</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lächle ich oft innerlich darüber aber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sorrio no coração várias vezes mas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я много раз смеюсь над этим в душе но</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nando mo kokoro de warau kedo</span></p><p begin="2:07.450" end="2:09.970" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:07.450" end="2:07.660">く</span><span begin="2:07.660" end="2:07.860">じ</span><span begin="2:07.860" end="2:08.040">け</span><span begin="2:08.040" end="2:08.280">そ</span><span begin="2:08.280" end="2:08.440">う</span><span begin="2:08.440" end="2:08.700">に</span><span begin="2:08.820" end="2:09.020">な</span><span begin="2:09.020" end="2:09.410">る</span><span begin="2:09.410" end="2:09.580">ん</span><span begin="2:09.580" end="2:09.770">だ</span><span begin="2:09.770" end="2:09.970">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">但我也曾几近挫败</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">但我也曾幾近挫敗</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I feel like I&apos;m going to break</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">꺾일 것만 같아져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je suis sur le point de flancher</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Siento que voy a quebrarme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich verliere fast den Mut</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sinto que vou acabar desanimando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я вот-вот сломаюсь</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kujikesou ni narunda yo</span></p><p begin="2:10.290" end="2:13.330" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:10.290" end="2:10.490">張</span><span begin="2:10.490" end="2:10.660">り</span><span begin="2:10.660" end="2:10.860">裂</span><span begin="2:10.860" end="2:11.020">け</span><span begin="2:11.020" end="2:11.260">そ</span><span begin="2:11.260" end="2:11.440">う</span><span begin="2:11.440" end="2:11.620">に</span><span begin="2:11.620" end="2:11.820">な</span><span begin="2:11.820" end="2:12.340">る</span><span begin="2:12.340" end="2:12.530">ん</span><span begin="2:12.530" end="2:12.930">だ</span><span begin="2:12.930" end="2:13.330">よ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">心也曾几近撕裂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">心也曾幾近撕裂</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I feel like I&apos;m going to be torn apart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">찢어질 것만 같아져</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Mon cœur est sur le point de se briser</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Siento que voy a estallar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich zerbreche fast daran</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Sinto que meu coração vai se partir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Моё сердце вот-вот разорвётся на части</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Harisakesou ni narunda yo</span></p><p begin="2:14.230" end="2:17.290" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:14.230" end="2:14.620">何</span><span begin="2:14.620" end="2:14.830">も</span><span begin="2:14.830" end="2:14.990">見</span><span begin="2:14.990" end="2:15.160">え</span><span begin="2:15.160" end="2:15.350">な</span><span begin="2:15.350" end="2:15.560">く</span><span begin="2:15.560" end="2:15.740">な</span><span begin="2:15.740" end="2:15.910">る</span><span begin="2:15.910" end="2:16.320">時</span><span begin="2:16.320" end="2:16.490">も</span><span begin="2:16.490" end="2:16.670">あ</span><span begin="2:16.670" end="2:16.850">る</span><span begin="2:16.850" end="2:17.060">ん</span><span begin="2:17.060" end="2:17.290">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">也曾有过眼前一片漆黑的时候</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">也曾有過眼前一片漆黑的時候</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">There are times when I can&apos;t see anything at all</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아무것도 보이지 않게 될 때도 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il y a des moments où je ne vois plus rien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hay momentos en los que no puedo ver nada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Manchmal kann ich überhaupt nichts mehr sehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Há momentos em que não consigo ver nada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Бывают моменты когда я ничего не вижу</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nani mo mienaku naru toki mo arunda</span></p><p begin="2:18.920" end="2:21.070" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:18.920" end="2:19.300">何</span><span begin="2:19.300" end="2:19.670">度</span><span begin="2:19.670" end="2:19.860">だ</span><span begin="2:19.860" end="2:20.040">っ</span><span begin="2:20.040" end="2:20.230">て</span><span begin="2:20.230" end="2:20.420">悔</span><span begin="2:20.420" end="2:20.620">や</span><span begin="2:20.620" end="2:20.820">ん</span><span begin="2:20.820" end="2:21.070">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论多少次懊悔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論多少次懊悔</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I regretted it over and over again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몇 번이고 후회했어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J&apos;ai regretté maintes et maintes fois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me arrepentí una y otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich habe es immer wieder bereut</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Me arrependi várias vezes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сколько бы раз я ни сожалела</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nando datte kuyanda</span></p><p begin="2:22.320" end="2:24.790" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:22.320" end="2:22.700">何</span><span begin="2:22.700" end="2:23.060">度</span><span begin="2:23.060" end="2:23.280">だ</span><span begin="2:23.280" end="2:23.440">っ</span><span begin="2:23.440" end="2:23.610">て</span><span begin="2:23.610" end="2:23.790">立</span><span begin="2:23.790" end="2:23.970">ち</span><span begin="2:23.970" end="2:24.190">止</span><span begin="2:24.190" end="2:24.370">ま</span><span begin="2:24.370" end="2:24.560">っ</span><span begin="2:24.560" end="2:24.790">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论多少次驻足</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論多少次駐足</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I stopped in my tracks over and over again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몇 번이고 멈춰 섰어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je me suis arrêté maintes et maintes fois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me detuve una y otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich bin immer wieder stehen geblieben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Parei no caminho várias vezes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Сколько бы раз я ни останавливалась</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nando datte tachidomatta</span></p><p begin="2:25.280" end="2:31.690" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:25.280" end="2:25.480">そ</span><span begin="2:25.480" end="2:25.650">の</span><span begin="2:25.650" end="2:26.070">度</span><span begin="2:26.070" end="2:26.380">に</span><span begin="2:26.820" end="2:27.000">あ</span><span begin="2:27.180" end="2:27.560">な</span><span begin="2:27.560" end="2:27.940">た</span><span begin="2:27.940" end="2:28.300">が</span><span begin="2:28.300" end="2:28.700">い</span><span begin="2:28.700" end="2:29.680">る</span><span begin="2:29.780" end="2:30.000">か</span><span begin="2:30.000" end="2:31.690">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">正因为每次都有你在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">正因為每次都有你在</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because you are there every single time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그럴 때마다 네가 있으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car à chaque fois tu es là</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque cada vez tú estás ahí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil du jedes Mal da bist</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque toda vez você estava lá</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь каждый раз ты был рядом</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono tabi ni anata ga iru kara</span></p><p begin="2:33.130" end="2:38.150" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:33.130" end="2:33.910">正</span><span begin="2:33.910" end="2:34.690">解</span><span begin="2:34.690" end="2:35.330">の</span><span begin="2:35.440" end="2:35.980">な</span><span begin="2:35.980" end="2:36.170">い</span><span begin="2:36.170" end="2:36.950">旅</span><span begin="2:36.950" end="2:37.230">に</span><span begin="2:37.230" end="2:37.680">し</span><span begin="2:37.680" end="2:38.000">よ</span><span begin="2:38.000" end="2:38.150">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这就将是一场没有标准答案的旅途</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這就將是一場沒有標準答案的旅途</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let&apos;s make it a journey with no right answer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">정답 없는 여행으로 하자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Faisons-en un voyage sans bonne réponse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hagamos que sea un viaje sin respuestas correctas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass uns daraus eine Reise ohne richtige Antwort machen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vamos transformar isso numa jornada sem respostas certas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть это будет путешествие где нет правильных ответов</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Seikai no nai tabi ni shiyou</span></p><p begin="2:38.800" end="2:45.120" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:38.800" end="2:39.210">変</span><span begin="2:39.210" end="2:39.400">わ</span><span begin="2:39.400" end="2:39.560">っ</span><span begin="2:39.560" end="2:39.730">て</span><span begin="2:39.730" end="2:39.950">い</span><span begin="2:39.950" end="2:40.100">く</span><span begin="2:40.100" end="2:40.330">日</span><span begin="2:40.330" end="2:40.710">々</span><span begin="2:40.710" end="2:41.140">に</span><span begin="2:41.800" end="2:42.180">嘆</span><span begin="2:42.180" end="2:42.680">く</span><span begin="2:42.680" end="2:43.120">必</span><span begin="2:43.120" end="2:43.680">要</span><span begin="2:43.680" end="2:44.010">は</span><span begin="2:44.260" end="2:44.430">な</span><span begin="2:44.430" end="2:44.600">い</span><span begin="2:44.600" end="2:44.810">か</span><span begin="2:44.810" end="2:45.120">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">没必要对变迁的岁月感到叹息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">沒必要對變遷的歲月感到嘆息</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because there is no need to lament the changing days</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">변해가는 나날에 한탄할 필요는 없으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Car il n&apos;y a pas lieu de déplorer les jours qui changent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque no hay necesidad de lamentar los días que cambian</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil du den sich verändernden Tagen nicht nachtrauern musst</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque não há necessidade de lamentar os dias que mudam</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ведь нет нужды горевать о меняющихся днях</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kawatte iku hibi ni nageku hitsuyou wa nai kara</span></p><p begin="2:45.900" end="2:50.290" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:45.900" end="2:47.320">諦</span><span begin="2:47.430" end="2:48.150">め</span><span begin="2:48.150" end="2:48.240">ち</span><span begin="2:48.240" end="2:48.630">ゃ</span><span begin="2:48.920" end="2:49.180">ダ</span><span begin="2:49.330" end="2:49.680">メ</span><span begin="2:49.680" end="2:49.880">だ</span><span begin="2:49.880" end="2:50.060">よ</span><span begin="2:50.060" end="2:50.290">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">“不能放弃啊”</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">「不能放棄啊」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Telling me I shouldn&apos;t give up</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">포기하면 안 된다고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En disant qu&apos;il ne faut pas abandonner</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Diciendo que no debo rendirme</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Gib bloß nicht auf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Dizendo que eu não devo desistir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Со словами не смей сдаваться</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Akiramecha dame da yo to</span></p><p begin="2:50.750" end="2:56.520" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:50.750" end="2:51.170">そ</span><span begin="2:51.170" end="2:51.530">の</span><span begin="2:51.530" end="2:52.290">声</span><span begin="2:52.290" end="2:52.610">が</span><span begin="2:52.710" end="2:53.060">鳴</span><span begin="2:53.480" end="2:53.830">る</span><span begin="2:53.830" end="2:55.330">方</span><span begin="2:55.330" end="2:56.520">へ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">朝着那个声音响起的方向</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">朝著那個聲音響起的方向</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Towards the direction where that voice rings</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 목소리가 울리는 쪽으로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Vers là où résonne cette voix</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hacia donde suena esa voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dorthin wo diese Stimme erklingt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Em direção de onde soa essa voz</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Туда где звучит этот голос</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono koe ga naru hou e</span></p><p begin="2:57.130" end="3:02.210" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:57.130" end="2:57.920">正</span><span begin="2:57.920" end="2:58.680">解</span><span begin="2:58.680" end="2:59.440">の</span><span begin="2:59.440" end="3:00.030">な</span><span begin="3:00.030" end="3:00.170">い</span><span begin="3:00.170" end="3:00.940">旅</span><span begin="3:00.940" end="3:01.260">を</span><span begin="3:01.260" end="3:01.670">し</span><span begin="3:01.670" end="3:02.080">よ</span><span begin="3:02.080" end="3:02.210">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">踏上这没有标准答案的旅途吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">踏上這沒有標準答案的旅途吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Let&apos;s go on a journey with no right answer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">정답 없는 여행을 하자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Faisons un voyage sans bonne réponse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hagamos un viaje sin respuestas correctas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lass uns eine Reise ohne richtige Antwort machen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vamos fazer uma jornada sem respostas certas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Давай отправимся в путешествие где нет правильных ответов</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Seikai no nai tabi o shiyou</span></p><p begin="3:02.800" end="3:09.180" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:02.800" end="3:03.160">魔</span><span begin="3:03.160" end="3:03.550">法</span><span begin="3:03.550" end="3:03.930">が</span><span begin="3:03.930" end="3:04.100">な</span><span begin="3:04.100" end="3:04.310">く</span><span begin="3:04.310" end="3:04.700">て</span><span begin="3:04.700" end="3:05.200">も</span><span begin="3:05.780" end="3:06.180">怖</span><span begin="3:06.180" end="3:06.560">が</span><span begin="3:06.560" end="3:06.700">る</span><span begin="3:06.700" end="3:07.110">必</span><span begin="3:07.110" end="3:07.700">要</span><span begin="3:07.700" end="3:07.990">は</span><span begin="3:08.240" end="3:08.440">な</span><span begin="3:08.440" end="3:08.630">い</span><span begin="3:08.630" end="3:08.820">ん</span><span begin="3:08.820" end="3:09.180">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即便没有魔法 也没必要感到恐惧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即便沒有魔法 也沒必要感到恐懼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even without magic there&apos;s no need to be afraid</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마법이 없어도 두려워할 필요는 없어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même sans magie il n&apos;y a pas lieu d&apos;avoir peur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque no haya magia no hay necesidad de tener miedo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch ohne Magie musst du keine Angst haben</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não há necessidade de ter medo mesmo sem magia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже без магии нет нужды бояться</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Mahou ga nakutemo kowagaru hitsuyou wa nainda</span></p><p begin="3:09.940" end="3:14.320" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:09.940" end="3:10.300">ね</span><span begin="3:10.300" end="3:10.690">え</span><span begin="3:10.690" end="3:11.180">ど</span><span begin="3:11.180" end="3:11.440">う</span><span begin="3:11.440" end="3:11.980">だ</span><span begin="3:11.980" end="3:12.160">い</span><span begin="3:12.160" end="3:12.560">こ</span><span begin="3:12.560" end="3:12.920">の</span><span begin="3:12.920" end="3:13.660">日</span><span begin="3:13.660" end="3:14.060">常</span><span begin="3:14.060" end="3:14.320">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">呐 觉得如何呢 这样的日常</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">吶 覺得如何呢 這樣的日常</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Hey what do you think of this everyday life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">있잖아 어때 이 일상은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Dis que penses-tu de ce quotidien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Oye qué te parece esta cotidianidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hey wie gefällt dir dieser Alltag</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ei o que você acha deste cotidiano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Эй как тебе эти будни</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nee doudai kono nichijou wa</span></p><p begin="3:14.780" end="3:20.470" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:14.780" end="3:14.980">こ</span><span begin="3:14.980" end="3:15.190">こ</span><span begin="3:15.190" end="3:15.560">で</span><span begin="3:15.560" end="3:15.910">は</span><span begin="3:15.910" end="3:16.150">ず</span><span begin="3:16.150" end="3:16.310">っ</span><span begin="3:16.310" end="3:16.460">と</span><span begin="3:16.460" end="3:16.990">一</span><span begin="3:17.430" end="3:17.740">人</span><span begin="3:17.740" end="3:17.820">じ</span><span begin="3:17.820" end="3:18.930">ゃ</span><span begin="3:18.930" end="3:19.290">な</span><span begin="3:19.290" end="3:20.470">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在这里 我们一直都不是孤单一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在這裡 我們一直都不是孤單一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I am never alone here</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">여기서는 계속 혼자가 아니야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ici on ne sera jamais seul</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aquí nunca estaré solo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hier bist du nie allein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aqui eu nunca estarei sozinha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Здесь я всегда буду не одна</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koko dewa zutto hitori janai</span></p><p begin="3:21.890" end="3:27.490" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:21.890" end="3:22.260">間</span><span begin="3:22.260" end="3:22.840">違</span><span begin="3:22.840" end="3:23.040">い</span><span begin="3:23.040" end="3:23.290">を</span><span begin="3:23.800" end="3:23.950">間</span><span begin="3:23.950" end="3:24.390">違</span><span begin="3:24.390" end="3:24.550">い</span><span begin="3:24.550" end="3:24.810">と</span><span begin="3:25.290" end="3:26.030">思</span><span begin="3:26.030" end="3:26.300">わ</span><span begin="3:26.410" end="3:27.010">な</span><span begin="3:27.010" end="3:27.200">い</span><span begin="3:27.200" end="3:27.490">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">别把错误仅仅当作错误</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">別把錯誤僅僅當作錯誤</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Don&apos;t think of mistakes as just mistakes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">잘못을 잘못이라 생각하지 마</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne considère pas une erreur comme une erreur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No pienses que un error es un error</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Halte einen Fehler nicht für einen Fehler</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não pense em um erro como sendo apenas um erro</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не считай ошибку ошибкой</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Machigai o machigai to omowanaide</span></p><p begin="3:27.900" end="3:33.440" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:27.900" end="3:29.060">涙</span><span begin="3:29.060" end="3:29.330">を</span><span begin="3:29.810" end="3:30.570">涙</span><span begin="3:30.570" end="3:30.840">で</span><span begin="3:31.310" end="3:31.680">満</span><span begin="3:31.680" end="3:31.990">た</span><span begin="3:31.990" end="3:32.410">さ</span><span begin="3:32.410" end="3:33.040">な</span><span begin="3:33.040" end="3:33.200">い</span><span begin="3:33.200" end="3:33.440">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">别让泪水仅仅充盈着泪水</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">別讓淚水僅僅充盈著淚水</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Don&apos;t fill tears with more tears</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">눈물을 눈물로 채우지 마</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ne noie pas tes larmes dans les larmes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">No llenes las lágrimas con lágrimas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Fülle Tränen nicht mit Tränen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Não preencha as lágrimas com mais lágrimas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Не наполняй слёзы слезами</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Namida o namida de mitasanaide</span></p><p begin="3:33.910" end="3:39.770" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:33.910" end="3:34.530">確</span><span begin="3:34.630" end="3:35.040">信</span><span begin="3:35.040" end="3:35.250">が</span><span begin="3:35.250" end="3:35.440">あ</span><span begin="3:35.440" end="3:35.650">る</span><span begin="3:35.760" end="3:36.050">そ</span><span begin="3:36.180" end="3:36.530">の</span><span begin="3:36.900" end="3:38.020">心</span><span begin="3:38.270" end="3:38.410">が</span><span begin="3:38.410" end="3:39.180">叫</span><span begin="3:39.180" end="3:39.370">ん</span><span begin="3:39.370" end="3:39.570">で</span><span begin="3:39.570" end="3:39.770">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">怀抱确信的那颗心在呐喊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">懷抱確信的那顆心在吶喊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That heart with conviction is screaming</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">확신이 있는 그 마음이 외치고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce cœur rempli de conviction hurle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ese corazón con convicción está gritando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieses Herz das sich sicher ist schreit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esse coração que tem certeza está gritando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Это уверенное сердце кричит</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kakushin ga aru sono kokoro ga sakenderu</span></p><p begin="3:41.240" end="3:44.580" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:41.240" end="3:41.430">こ</span><span begin="3:41.430" end="3:41.620">こ</span><span begin="3:41.620" end="3:41.820">な</span><span begin="3:41.820" end="3:42.030">ら</span><span begin="3:42.220" end="3:42.420">も</span><span begin="3:42.420" end="3:42.620">う</span><span begin="3:42.770" end="3:43.140">一</span><span begin="3:43.140" end="3:43.300">人</span><span begin="3:43.300" end="3:43.370">じ</span><span begin="3:43.370" end="3:43.700">ゃ</span><span begin="3:43.700" end="3:44.350">な</span><span begin="3:44.350" end="3:44.580">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在这里 就再也不是孤身一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在這裡 就再也不是孤身一人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">If it&apos;s here I am not alone anymore</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">여기라면 더 이상 혼자가 아니야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ici on n&apos;est plus seul</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si es aquí ya no estoy solo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hier bist du nicht mehr allein</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se for aqui não estarei mais sozinha</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Здесь я уже не одна</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Koko nara mou hitori janai</span></p></div></body></tt>